'''钋化镁''' (MgPo) 是[[镁|镁]]和[[钋|钋]]组成的盐。它是一种[[钋化物|钋化物]]，是一系列化学性质稳定的钋化合物<ref name="Greenwood&Earnshaw">{{Greenwood&Earnshaw1st|page=899}}</ref>。

==制备==
钋化镁可以由加热金属镁和钋到 300–400 °C 而成。<ref name="Bagnall">{{cite book |title=Advances in Inorganic Chemistry and Radiochemistry |chapter=The Chemistry of Polonium |last1=Bagnall |first1=K. W. |year=1962 |publisher=[[Academic_Press|Academic Press]] |location=New York |isbn=9780120236046 |pages=197–230 |accessdate=June 17, 2012 |url=https://www.google.com/books?id=8qePsa3V8GQC}}</ref>

==结构==
钋化镁有[[红砷镍矿|NiAs]] 结构， [[晶格参数|晶格参数]]为 ''a'' = 434.5 pm 和 ''c'' = 707.7 pm。<ref name="Bagnall"/><ref name="Greenwood&Earnshaw"/> 它在[[钋化物|钋化物]]中是不寻常的，因为它和对应的[[硫化物|硫化物]]、[[硒化物|硒化物]]和[[碲化物|碲化物]]{{le|同构（晶体学）|isomorphism (crystallography)|同构}}。在所有钋化物中，只有[[钋化汞|钋化汞]] (HgPo) 也有这个性质。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Witteman |first1=W. G. |last2=Giorgi |first2=A. L. |last3=Vier |first3=D. T. |year=1960 |title=The Preparation and Identification of Some Intermetallic Compounds of Polonium |journal=[[Journal_of_Physical_Chemistry|Journal of Physical Chemistry]] |volume=64 |issue=4 |pages=434–440 |publisher=[[American_Chemical_Society|American Chemical Society]] |doi= 10.1021/j100833a014|osti=4190680 }}</ref>

